                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8189" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0380</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2015 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">相契还是相异？——Z分公司员工心理契约的形成与违背</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Similarity or Differences: The Formation and Violation of Psychological Contracts of the Employees of Z Branch</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王晓丹，郭跃，郭磊</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东北师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Z分公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">心理契约；人力资源管理；职业发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">psychological contract; human resource management; career development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">心理契约是员工和企业双方对相互责任的信念，具体体现为双方对相互责任义务的主观约定。建立良好的心理契约对组织与员工双方都有着重要意义。本案例以Z分公司为背景，围绕赵晓明、李炎、陈华三位员工入职以来的工作经历，通过描写Z分公司三位员工入职以来的工作表现和心路变化历程，刻画了典型的心理契约形成过程和影响因素。旨在帮助学生理解心理契约的涵义，并认识到心理契约对员工和组织的意义；结合三位新员工的工作经历和心理历程，引导学生理解心理契约的形成过程及影响因素，理解心理契约的形成和变化规律；进而明白心理契约的存在及它对组织人力资源管理的影响，良好的心理契约形成对于员工工作积极性的意义，理解心理契约相关理论，并能在组织管理中很好地建立与员工的良性心理契约。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Psychological contract is the belief of employees and enterprises on the mutual responsibility, which is embodied in the subjective agreement between the two parties on the mutual responsibility and obligation. The establishment of a good psychological contract is of great significance to both the organization and the employees. This case takes Z branch as the background, centers on the work experience of three employees, Zhao Xiaoming, Li Yan and Chen Hua, and portrays the typical process of psychological contract formation and influencing factors by describing the work performance and the course of change of heart of the three employees of Z branch since they joined the company. It aims to help students understand the meaning of psychological contract and recognize the significance of psychological contract to employees and organizations; combined with the work experience and psychological journey of the three new employees, it guides students to understand the formation process and influencing factors of the psychological contract, and the formation and change rule of the psychological contract; and then understand the existence of the psychological contract and its impact on the organization&#39;s human resource management, and the meaning of the good psychological contract formation for the employee work Then they will understand the existence of psychological contract and its impact on human resource management, the significance of good psychological contract formation for employees&#39; work motivation, understand the theory of psychological contract, and be able to establish a good psychological contract with employees in the management of the organization.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">心理契约理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
